    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Doujutsu)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 33</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You pour a powerful surge of killing intent into a melee attack you make against the target. If the attack hits, the subject suffers such a powerful surge of fear that it is immediately reduced to -1 HP and starts dying. If the target succeeds at their save, they are instead cowering for 1 round.</p>\n\n\n\n",
